title: Smart Watch, GRDE Fitness Tracker Watch, Bluetooth 5.0 Activity Tracker Full Touch Screen Smartwatch 5ATM Waterproof for Man / Woman with Heart Rate, Sleep Monitor, Step & Calorie Counter, SMS Call Notification Compatible with iPhone Sumsung - Black
description: [ Physical Health Tracking ] GRDE smart watche is designed to monitor and understand your physical health, which can monitor your heart rate, count steps, track calories, monitor sleep and more. Not only that, when you sit for a long time without getting up, the smart fitness tracker will vibrate to remind you to relax. It keeps an eye on your health and reminds you so you can improve your habits and have a healthy body. (Note: The data are only for reference and not for medical use.) [ Long-life Battery & Large Screen ] With a built-in low-power Bluetooth chip and a 210 mAh high-capacity battery, the GRDE smart watch can be used for up to 10 days and 45 days of standby time in just 2 hours of charging. The 1.3-inch HD color screen features a full touch screen and button operation for giving you a better and more convenient experience. [ 14 sports modes & 5ATM Waterproof ] The fitness tracker watch has 14 sport modes, such as running, cycling, swimming, hiking and yoga etc. Connect the watch to your phone via the VeryFitPro APP, and GPS tracking will accurately calculates your steps, distance and route. 5ATM waterproof rating allows you to swim freely and monitor your movements within 50 meters of water depth. [ Women's Health Care & Breathing Training ] In addition to regular exercise and fitness tracking, there is also a monitoring physiological period function designed specifically for women. Record the physiological cycle via APP can predict the ovulation cycle, and remind you of the physiological period to help you improve your healthier lifestyle. The breathing function also allow you to train your lung capacity and exercise your lungs. [ Messages & Calls Reminder ] When the smartwatch connects to your phone via an APP, it will vibrate to alert you to phone calls, text messages, emails or instant messages (Facebook, Twitter, WhatsApp etc). The fitness tracker won't answer the phone, but it can refuse. It will keep you from missing anything important.
